@prefix fhir: <http://hl7.org/fhir/> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .

# - resource -------------------------------------------------------------------

<https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/CapabilityStatement/agrosus-server-capabilities> a fhir:CapabilityStatement ;
  fhir:nodeRole fhir:treeRoot ;
  fhir:Resource.id [ fhir:value "agrosus-server-capabilities"] ;
  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narrativa gerada: CapabilityStatement agrosus-server-capabilities</b></p><a name=\"agrosus-server-capabilities\"> </a><a name=\"hcagrosus-server-capabilities\"> </a><h2 id=\"title\">Requisitos de capacidade do servidor AgroSUS</h2><ul><li>Guia de implementação Versão: 0.1.0 </li><li>Versão FHIR: 4.0.1 </li><li>Formatos suportados: <code>json</code>, <code>xml</code></li><li>Publicado em: 2026-07-20 </li><li>Publicado por: Fatec Ferraz de Vasconcelos </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Nota para os implementadores: Capacidades FHIR</strong></p><p>Qualquer capacidade FHIR pode ser \"permitida\" pelo sistema, exceto se for explicitamente assinalada como \"NÃO DEVE\". Alguns itens são marcados como MAY no Guia de Implementação para destacar a sua potencial relevância para o caso de utilização.</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"shallIGs\">DEVERÁ suportar os seguintes guias de implementação</h3><ul><li><a href=\"index.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/ImplementationGuide/io.github.jefersonrl.agrosus</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"rest\">Capacidades FHIR RESTful</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>API FHIR R4 para cadastro e acompanhamento longitudinal do trabalhador rural. O aplicativo do ACS deve enviar a visita por Bundle transaction; o dashboard da UBS consulta os dados pelos parâmetros declarados neste CapabilityStatement.</p>\n</div><div class=\"lead\"><em>Security</em></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\">Ativar CORS: sim</div><div class=\"col-lg-6\">Security services supported: </div></div><blockquote><div><p>A implementação deve utilizar TLS, autenticação, autorização por função e registro de auditoria. CORS deve ser limitado às origens autorizadas em produção.</p>\n</div></blockquote><div class=\"lead\"><em>Resumo das interações a nível do sistema</em></div><ul><li>Apoia o <code>transaction</code>interação descrita da seguinte forma:<div><p>Aceita a transação AgroSUS de sincronização da visita do ACS de forma atômica.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div><h3 id=\"resourcesCap1\">Capacidades por recurso/perfil</h3><h4 id=\"resourcesSummary1\">Resumo</h4><p>A tabela de resumo enumera os recursos que fazem parte desta configuração e, para cada recurso, enumera-os:</p><ul><li>Os perfis relevantes (se existirem)</li><li>As interações suportadas por cada recurso (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>só estão presentes se pelo menos um dos recursos os suportar.</li><li><span>Os parâmetros de pesquisa obrigatórios, recomendados e alguns opcionais (se existirem). </span></li><li>Os recursos ligados activados para <code>_include</code></li><li>Os outros recursos activados para <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>As operações sobre o recurso (se existirem)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Tipo de recurso</b></th><th><b>Perfil</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET um recurso (interação de leitura)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET todo o conjunto de recursos do tipo (interação de pesquisa)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT uma nova versão do recurso (interação de atualização)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST um novo recurso (criar interação)\">C</b></th><th><b title=\"Parâmetros de pesquisa necessários e recomendados\">Pesquisas</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operações</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#Patient1-1\">Patient</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-patient.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-patient</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>identifier, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Practitioner1-2\">Practitioner</a></td><td>Perfis suportados<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-acs.html\">Agente Comunitário de Saúde AgroSUS</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-profissional-ubs.html\">Profissional Assistencial da UBS AgroSUS</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#PractitionerRole1-3\">PractitionerRole</a></td><td>Perfis suportados<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-acs-role.html\">Função do ACS no AgroSUS</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-profissional-ubs-role.html\">Função do Profissional Assistencial da UBS AgroSUS</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>practitioner, organization, role, active</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Organization1-4\">Organization</a></td><td>Perfis suportados<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-ubs.html\">Unidade Básica de Saúde AgroSUS</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-laboratorio.html\">Laboratório AgroSUS</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier, name, active</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Questionnaire1-5\">Questionnaire</a></td><td> </td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>url, version, status</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#QuestionnaireResponse1-6\">QuestionnaireResponse</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-anamnese-response.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-anamnese-response</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>subject, encounter, author, authored, status</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Encounter1-7\">Encounter</a></td><td>Perfis suportados<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-visita-acs.html\">Visita do ACS AgroSUS</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-atendimento-ubs.html\">Atendimento Clínico da UBS AgroSUS</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, date, status, participant</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#ServiceRequest1-8\">ServiceRequest</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-solicitacao-exame.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-solicitacao-exame</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, authored, requester, status, code</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Observation1-9\">Observation</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-resultado-laboratorial.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-resultado-laboratorial</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, date, code, status, based-on</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#DiagnosticReport1-10\">DiagnosticReport</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-laudo-laboratorial.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-laudo-laboratorial</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, date, code, status, based-on</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Condition1-11\">Condition</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-intoxicacao-pesticida.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-intoxicacao-pesticida</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, clinical-status, verification-status, code, onset-date</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#CarePlan1-12\">CarePlan</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-plano-acompanhamento.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-plano-acompanhamento</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, status, date, category</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Provenance1-13\">Provenance</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-provenance.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-provenance</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>target, agent, recorded</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#AuditEvent1-14\">AuditEvent</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-audit-event.html\">https://jefersonrl.github.io/AgroSUS-FHIR/StructureDefinition/agrosus-audit-event</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>agent, date, entity, action</td><td/><td/><td/></tr></tbody></table></div><hr/><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Patient1-1\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>Patient</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Perfil do sistema de base</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-patient.html\">Paciente AgroSUS</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformidade do perfil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code>, <code>local</code></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>create</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>identifier</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Localiza o trabalhador por CPF ou CNS usando system|value.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>name</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Practitioner1-2\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>Practitioner</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Recurso FHIR principal</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html\">Practitioner</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Perfis suportados</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-acs.html\">Agente Comunitário de Saúde AgroSUS</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-profissional-ubs.html\">Profissional Assistencial da UBS AgroSUS</a></p></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>identifier</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>name</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"PractitionerRole1-3\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>PractitionerRole</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Recurso FHIR principal</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitionerrole.html\">PractitionerRole</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Perfis suportados</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-acs-role.html\">Função do ACS no AgroSUS</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-profissional-ubs-role.html\">Função do Profissional Assistencial da UBS AgroSUS</a></p></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>practitioner</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>organization</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>role</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>active</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Organization1-4\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>Organization</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Recurso FHIR principal</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html\">Organization</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Perfis suportados</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-ubs.html\">Unidade Básica de Saúde AgroSUS</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-laboratorio.html\">Laboratório AgroSUS</a></p></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>identifier</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>name</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>active</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Questionnaire1-5\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>Questionnaire</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Recurso FHIR principal</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/questionnaire.html\">Questionnaire</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>url</td><td><code>uri</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>version</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>status</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"QuestionnaireResponse1-6\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>QuestionnaireResponse</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Perfil do sistema de base</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-agrosus-anamnese-response.html\">Resposta da Anamnese AgroSUS</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformidade do perfil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code>, <code>local</code></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>create</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Parâmetros de pesquisa</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformidade</th><th>Parâmetro</th><th>Tipo</th><th>Documentação</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>subject</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>encounter</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>author</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>authored</td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>status</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Encounter1-7\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformidade do recurso: unspecified </span>Encounter</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Recurso FHIR principal</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/encounter.html\">Encounter</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Política de referência</span><br/><code>literal</code>, <code>local</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Resumo da interação</span><br/><ul><li>Apoios <code>create</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><